| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1371 — Recovery Inhibition (fog)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d5d7bc3e-c6ad-5a36-ae73-f2bf787ff36e"
